title: Keep The Right Perspective
itunes:title: Keep The Right Perspective
description:
We all want to live an extraordinary life, but do we realize that extraordinary begins with who we are? God says you are His masterpiece, an original creation. Only you can do what He has called you to do. Stay faithful. God is preparing you for an extraordinary future!

Learn more about your ad-choices at https://www.iheartpodcastnetwork.com
